<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>We Are At Your Service</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        /* Navbar Styling */
        header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 40px;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            color: #fff;
            
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .header-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 0 20px;
            
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        header p {
            padding-left: 10px;
            font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .logo img {
            margin-top: 15px;
            height: 200px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 30px;
            font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin-right: 50px;

        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #e2510d;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-family: 'Bookman, URW Bookman L, serif';
            font-weight: bold;
            font-variant: small-caps;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #090909;
            text-decoration: underline;
            text-shadow: #1a1a1a;
        }

        .header-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 0 20px;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        
        .first {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #1a73e8, #003366);
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .first h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .carousel {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            display: flex;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .carousel-track {
            display: flex;
            width: max-content;
            animation: scroll-continuous 10s linear infinite;
        }

        .carousel img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-right: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        @keyframes scroll-continuous {
            0% { transform: translateX(100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        }

        .carousel-track:hover {
            animation-play-state: paused;
        }


        /* Container and main content */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 80px auto 0; /* Add margin to avoid content overlap with navbar */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            flex-grow: 1; /* Allow the container to grow and push footer to the bottom */
        }
        header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: linear-gradient(to right,#1a73e8,#003366);
        }
        /* New grid structure */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .grid .container-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            height: 250px;
        }
        .container-box h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: linear-gradient(to right,#1a73e8,#003366);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .container-box p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to right,#1a73e8,#003366);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(to right,#1a73e8,#003366);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .button span {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        /* Dropdown for Predefined Messages */
        .dropdown {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        /* Chatbox Styling */
        .chatbox-container {
            position: relative;
        }
        .chatbox {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #fff;
            resize: none;
            padding-right: 50px; /* Space for send button */
        }
        /* Small Send Button within the chatbox */
        .send-button-inside {
            position: absolute;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right,#1a73e8,#003366);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .send-button-inside:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            position: relative;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .navbar nav a {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
            .grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <header>
        <div class="header-container">
            <div class="logo">
                 <img src="soulsyncnew-removebg-preview.png" >
            </div>
    
            <nav class="nav-links">
                <a href="./aboutus">About Us</a>
                <a href="./contactus">Contact Us</a>
            </nav>
    
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="first">
            <h1>"We Are At Your Service!!!"</h1>
            <div class="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-track">
                    <img src="vol1.jpg" alt="Image 1">
                    <img src="vol2.avif" alt="Image 2">
                    <img src="vol3.jpg" alt="Image 3">
                    <img src="vol4.avif" alt="Image 4">
                    <img src="vol5.jpg" alt="Image 5">
                    <img src="vol6.jpg" alt="Image 1">
                    <img src="vol7.jpg" alt="Image 2">
                    <img src="vol8.jpg" alt="Image 3">
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <!-- Updated grid layout with two sections -->
        <div class="grid">
            <!-- Top section with Predefined Message and Quick Chat -->
            <div class="container-box">
                <h2>Predefined Message</h2>
                <!-- Dropdown with a placeholder SOS message -->
                <select class="dropdown">
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select SOS Message</option>
                    <option value="earthquake">Earthquake</option>
                    <option value="landslide">Landslide</option>
                    <option value="flood">Flood</option>
                    <option value="tsunami">Tsunami</option>
                    <option value="wildfire">Wildfire</option>
                    <option value="medical_assistance">Medical Assistance</option>
                </select>
                <div class="button">
                    <span>Send Message</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container-box">
                <h2>Quick Chat</h2>
                <div class="chatbox-container">
                    <!-- Chatbox with Send button inside -->
                    <textarea class="chatbox" placeholder="Type your message here..."></textarea>
                    <button class="send-button-inside">➤</button> <!-- Send symbol -->
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Bottom section with Funds and Help -->
            <div class="container-box">
                <h2>Funds</h2>
                <p>Relief yourself from th econamic crices by PM Relief Funds!!! We Are With You!!!</p>
                <div class="button">
                    <a href="https://pmnrf.gov.in/en/"><span style="color: white;">Get Relief Funds</span></a> 
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container-box">
                <h2>Help</h2>
                <p>Never feel helpless make yourself aware during the situation with the assistence!!!</p>
                <div class="button">
                    <a href="index.html"><span style="color: white;">Get Assistance</span></a> 
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 We Are At Your Service. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
